text=!! Testing Suspend2 on PPC, Powerbook G4²²!!! Kernel: 2.6.13-rc6²Attach:linuxbest2.jpg²²!!! Kernel 2.6.12.2²Works great. Apply following patches with Kernel 2.6.12.2:²# http://www.suspend2.net/downloads/all/software-suspend-2.1.9.5-for-2.6.12.tar.bz2²# http://soulinfo.com/~hugang/kernel/linux-2.6.12/fix_dup_nosave -> this should fix copy back hang in ppc.²# http://soulinfo.com/~hugang/kernel/linux-2.6.12/split_stack_moving -> trying to making switch stack smooth.²# http://soulinfo.com/~hugang/tmp/gcc-3.3.5-fix²²Many thanks to Gang Hu!²²Attach:linuxbest.jpg\\²The requested files by suspend2; ²Attach:vmlinux.txt Attach:suspend2.h.txt Attach:atomic_copy.c.txt²²# suspend²# yaboot: new noresume2 init=/bin/sh²# mount -t proc none /proc²# cd /proc/²# cd software_suspend/²# swapon -a²# echo "swap:/dev/hda4" > resume2²# echo 1 > disable_encryption²# echo lzf > compressor²# echo 3 > default_console_level²# echo 1 > do_suspend²# resume²# yaboot: new resume2=swap:/dev/hda4
